  "title": "Kitchen Crew",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Involve kitchen operations from food preparation, cook to final production</li>\n  <li>Food preparation will be in accordance with daily operations</li>\n  <li>Keep up to date with the current promotions and new items on the menu</li>\n  <li>Maintain a clean and safe working environment, adhering to kitchen Standard Operation Procedures (SOPs)</li>\n  <li>Take guest orders and present the food to them with good customer service</li>\n  <li>Maintain food quality and standard any other duties as assigned by the Food Manager</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Prior cooking experiences would be an added advantage</li>\n  <li>5-days work week including weekends (44 hours per week and rotating shifts in between 7am to 12am)</li>\n  <li>Possessing hygiene certificate will be an added advantage</li>\n</ul>",
